        "title": "Thursday news quiz: Trump is unwise, an emperor dies and a €1m raffle prize",
        "link": "https://www.theguardian.com/lifeandstyle/2026/apr/16/the-guardian-thursday-quiz-general-knowledge-topical-news-trivia-243",
        "published": "Thu, 16 Apr 2026 05:00:49 GMT",
